Interface LinkEnd

All Superinterfaces:

All Known Subinterfaces:
Contained, Container, Reference
All Known Implementing Classes:
LinkEndImpl
public interface LinkEnd
extends Value

This interface represents a link end of an object in the framework object model.

XMIObjects have values that are defined by the features in the corresponding XMIClass. The XMI name of a value is the XMI name of a feature in an XMIClass.

The subclasses of this class represent values of type Value.REFERENCE, Value.CONTAINER, and Value.CONTAINED.
